Q2: Take three variables as input and add them without using the + operator (Use your head for this)

Start
Print"Enter number 1"
Input n1
Print"Enter number 2"
Input n2
Print"Enter number 3"
Input n3
Set Sum to n1-(-n2)-(-n3)
print Sum
End
