Q3: Create a small calculator which only does ‘+’ or ‘-‘Operations. (Hint: Take three variable inputs with
one being used for the operator)

Start
Print"Enter number 1"
Input n1 as integer
Print"Enter number 2"
Input n2 as integer
Print"Enter the operator"
Int c;
if(c = +)
print n1+n2
else if(c = -)
print n1-n2

End
